descriptions.see_description: In the input, you should see... a shape on a black background
descriptions.grid_description: The output grid size...is the same.
descriptions.do_description: To make the output, you have to...keep the shape color the same. Fill any areas contained within the shape red and flood the black background with green.

descriptions.see_description: In the input, you should see... a colored grid all the same color with lines one block wide
descriptions.grid_description: The output grid size... the same as the input grid
descriptions.do_description: To make the output, you have to... fill in all holes with red and fill the outside with green

descriptions.see_description: In the input, you should see...yellow intersecting lines on a black grid
descriptions.grid_description: The output grid size... is the same as the input
descriptions.do_description: To make the output, you have to...fill all region that have been surrounded with yellow lines in red.
